# AI-Powered SaaS Analytics Platform

A multi-tenant analytics app: companies sign up, log KPI metrics, and
generate AI-written executive summaries from their data using GPT-4.

## Architecture
- **Backend:** FastAPI + PostgreSQL, JWT auth, Row-Level Security for
  tenant isolation, GPT-4o for summary generation.
- **Frontend:** Next.js (App Router), plain fetch calls to the API.

## How multi-tenancy works
Every tenant-owned table (`users`, `metrics`, `ai_summaries`) has a
`tenant_id` column and a Postgres Row-Level Security (RLS) policy. On
every authenticated request, the backend sets a session variable
(`app.current_tenant`) to the caller's tenant ID (decoded from their
JWT). Postgres then transparently filters every query to that tenant
— enforced at the database layer, not just app code.

